snippet.title: Grimoire Groves - Offiical Gameplay Trailer | The MIX Fall Showcase 2024
snippet.description: Players will become a masterful witch in Grimoire Groves, a cozy roguelite dungeon crawler. Craft spells, discover a diverse set of plant types, and restore the magical forest once again. Take a look at this new trailer to get a look at new enemies, plants, and more. Grimoire Groves is launching on March 6, 2025 for PC (Steam).
